on><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:46:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/us/us-plans-restore-tariffs-dominant-solar-technology-sources-say-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>F1重返中国面临新挑战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/f1-faces-fresh-challenge-return-china-2024-04-17/</link><description>一级方程式赛车自 2019 年以来首次重返中国，即使是世界冠军马克斯·维斯塔潘 (Max Verstappen) 在这条 15 年前为他的红牛车队赢得首场大奖赛胜利的赛道上也面临着新的挑战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 17:39:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/f1-faces-fresh-challenge-return-china-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>一级方程式中国大奖赛统计</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/formula-one-statistics-chinese-grand-prix-2024-04-17/</link><description>周日在上海国际赛车场举行的中国一级方程式大奖赛世界锦标赛第五轮的统计数据：</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:07:32 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/formula-one-statistics-chinese-grand-prix-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>部长称意大利正在与中国东风等公司就汽车工厂事宜进行谈判</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-with-chinas-dongfeng-others-over-auto-plant-minister-says-2024-04-17/</link><description>意大利工业部长阿道夫·乌尔索周三表示，意大利正在与中国东风汽车等公司进行谈判，以吸引除 Stellantis 之外的另一家主要汽车制造商来到该国。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 16:04:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/italy-talks-with-chinas-dongfeng-others-over-auto-plant-minister-says-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>ASML高管预计中国需求将保持强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-executives-expect-chinese-demand-remain-strong-2024-04-17/</link><description>荷兰计算机芯片设备制造商 ASML 的高管周三表示，他们预计中国客户的需求将保持强劲，“大约”占该公司积压订单的 20%。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asml-executives-expect-chinese-demand-remain-strong-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国贸易长官呼吁采取“果断”行动保护电动汽车行业免受中国影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ustr-tai-calls-decisive-action-shield-ev-sector-china-2024-04-17/</link><description>美国贸易代表凯瑟琳·戴周三表示，美国必须采取“果断”行动，保护电动汽车免受中国补贴的竞争，她正在完成对特朗普时代中国关税的审查，并考虑乔·拜登总统关于提高进口关税的呼吁中国钢铁。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 15:12:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/ustr-tai-calls-decisive-action-shield-ev-sector-china-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>美国承认日本和韩国对货币贬值的“严重”担忧</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-japan-korea-finance-leaders-launch-first-trilateral-meeting-2024-04-17/</link><description>美国、日本和韩国同意在周三的首次三边金融对话中就外汇市场进行“密切磋商”，回应了东京和首尔对其货币近期大幅贬值的担忧。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 14:49:44 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/us-japan-korea-finance-leaders-launch-first-trilateral-meeting-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>中国球迷希望周能在主场首秀中摆脱糟糕的状态</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/chinese-fans-hope-zhou-can-shrug-off-poor-form-home-debut-2024-04-17/</link><description>周冠宇的中国车迷希望中国第一位也是唯一一位一级方程式赛车手能够摆脱糟糕的表现，在主场首秀中大放异彩，以回应那些认为他的护照是他开车的主要原因的批评者。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 13:51:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/sports/formula1/chinese-fans-hope-zhou-can-shrug-off-poor-form-home-debut-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>德中签署汽车数据共享联合声明</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-joint-declaration-car-data-sharing-2024-04-17/</link><description>德国和中国签署了一项在自动驾驶和互联驾驶方面进行合作的联合声明，德国希望这将使汽车制造商能够将数据从中国传输到德国，这对于在华外国企业来说是一个有争议的话题。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 12:43:26 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/germany-china-sign-joint-declaration-car-data-sharing-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟商会主席警告称，中国和欧盟的贸易紧张局势可能引发全面贸易战</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/china-eu-trade-tensions-risk-full-trade-war-european-chamber-president-warns-2024-04-17/</link><description>欧洲商业游说团体负责人周三警告说，在德国总理向北京表达欧洲担忧的第二天，随着保护主义浪潮的高涨，中国和欧洲面临“慢动作火车事故”，有可能演变成一场全面的贸易战。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 11:54:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/china-eu-trade-tensions-risk-full-trade-war-european-chamber-president-warns-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>白宫称对中国金属征收新关税不会影响通胀</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/new-tariffs-chinese-metals-wont-impact-inflation-white-house-says-2024-04-17/</link><description>白宫经济顾问贾里德·伯恩斯坦周三表示，拜登政府正在考虑对中国金属产品大幅提高关税，这不会影响美国的通胀，而且对于国家安全来说是必要的。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 11:47:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/new-tariffs-chinese-metals-wont-impact-inflation-white-house-says-2024-04-17/</guid></item><item><title>国际货币基金组织通过改变贷款政策来遏制中国债务协议的拖延</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-board-backs-key-change-lending-into-official-arrears-policy-2024-04-17/</link><description>国际货币基金组织执行董事会支持一项关键变革，以赋予其更多自由来支持陷入危机的国家，即使与中国等大债权国政府的债务重新谈判仍在进行中。</description><pubDate>Wed, 17 Apr 2024 11:07:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/imf-board-backs-key-change-lending-into-official-arrears-policy-2024-04-17/</guid></item></channel></rss>